We also collect information about your shopping carts on our websites. Information includes cart items, quantities and variables. This applies to unpurchased and purchased carts.

When you register an account with us, your email will be automatically added to our mailing list. We will send you important notices or activities for your account, additionally, we might also send you advertising materials about our products or services. You can opt-out of any of the marketing services using the links below.

When we talk about ‚ÄúPersonal Information‚Äù in this Privacy Policy, we are talking both about Device Information and Order Information.

HOW DO WE USE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?

We use the Order Information that we collect generally to fulfil any orders placed through the Site (including processing your payment information, arranging for shipping, and providing you with invoices and/or order confirmations). Additionally, we use this Order Information to:

‚Äì Communicate with you;
‚Äì Screen our orders for potential risk or fraud; and
‚Äì When in line with the preferences you have shared with us, provide you with information or advertising relating to our products or services.
‚Äì Provide the requested services to you.

We use the Device Information that we collect to help us screen for potential risk and fraud (in particular, your IP address), and more generally to improve and optimize our Site (for example, by generating analytics about how our customers browse and interact with the Site, and to assess the success of our marketing and advertising campaigns).

We also use ‚ÄúCookies‚Äù stored by social media to provide services through social media such as Facebook live chat. These information will not be sent to us if you did not interact with the services.

SHARING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION

We share your Personal Information with third parties to help us use your Personal Information, as described above. For example, we use Stripe to power our online store‚Äìyou can read more about how Stripe uses your Personal Information here: https://www.stripe.com/privacy. We also use Google Analytics to help us understand how our customers use the Site ‚Äî you can read more about how Google uses your Personal Information here: https://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/. You can also opt-out of Google Analytics here: https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout.

